    "Goel et al. (2021) proposed an optimized GAN to generate synthetic chest CT images of COVID-19 disease.",
    "The optimized GAN utilizes a CGAN with Whale Optimization Algorithm (WOA) (Mirjalili and Lewis 2016) to optimize its hyperparameters.",
    "A flow of the Whale optimization algorithm is shown in Fig. 25.",
    "In this algorithm, the hunting trick of (21) g(, w) = g(, w) + M (w) and h(, w) = h(, w) + M (𝜃) (22) humpback whales is adapted to optimize the prey's location.",
    "This hunting trick determines the generator's best search agents with the given discriminator."
